 &lt;a href="http://polldaddy.com/poll/3700086/"&gt;No dia 17 de Setembro (Assembleia Municipal) já haverá conclusões do inquérito à HPEM?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:9px;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://polldaddy.com/features-surveys/"&gt;survey software&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
