&lt;/div&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/queluz/~4/fuHploZY2hc" height="1" width="1"/&gt;

&lt;div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_Yn7PBr-hdKs/TCIsKv1-NeI/AAAAAAAAFyw/oRd4_pAvcxk/s1600/smas.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: right; float: right; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 1em;"&gt;&lt;img border="0" height="131" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_Yn7PBr-hdKs/TCIsKv1-NeI/AAAAAAAAFyw/oRd4_pAvcxk/s200/smas.jpg" width="200" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;A empresa Serviços Municipalizados de Água e Saneamento de Sintra aderiu este mês às redes sociais. Com conta no Facebook e conta no &lt;a href="http://twitter.com/smassintra"&gt;Twitter&lt;/a&gt; os SMAS Sintra vão ao encontro dos cidadãos. &lt;br /&gt;
